headline.print_headline: Jason Millard Disqualified From US Open
headline.main: Jason Millard Disqualified From US Open

lead_paragraph: Jason Millard was disqualified from the U.S. Open on Saturday after reporting a self-imposed penalty for grounding his club in a bunker in sectional qualifying.
